<item>Dried fruits, beans, lentils, potatoes, winter squash (acorn, butternut), spinach, broccoli, beet greens, avocados</item>
<item>Fish, meat, poultry, eggs, dairy products</item>
<item>Milk, yogurt, cheese, eggs, lean beef and pork, organ meats (beef liver), chicken breast, salmon</item>
